# Frontend env vars — copy to .env.local and fill in.
#
# Used by the FacilityCard to fetch Google Static Street View photos of
# clicked cooling centres, libraries, food banks, community centres, and
# clinics. Without it, the card falls back to a kind-specific illustration.
#
# How to get one:
#   1. https://console.cloud.google.com/google/maps-apis
#   2. Enable "Street View Static API" and "Maps Static API"
#   3. Create an API key; restrict it to HTTP referrers for your domain
#
# Billing: $7 per 1000 photo requests. With ~30 facilities, a first session
# is roughly $0.20. Cache by domain/referrer for production deployment.
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
